projectConfig..gitattributes:
# Set default to normalize line endings
* text=auto eol=lf

# Force LF for text files that should never have CRLF
*.ts text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf

# PowerShell scripts
*.ps1 text eol=lf

# Binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.vsix binary
projectConfig..editorconfig:
root = true

# All files
[*]
charset = utf-8
end_of_line = lf
insert_final_newline = true
trim_trailing_whitespace = true

# TypeScript/JavaScript
[*.{ts,js,json}]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 4

# Markdown
[*.md]
trim_trailing_whitespace = false
indent_size = 2
